    <!-- Data ingestion -->
    <mxCell id="dataingestion" value="&lt;b&gt;DATA INGESTION (runs continuously, updated hourly)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Source 1 — EIA API v2 (TVA Grid):&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Hourly generation in MWh by fuel type (Coal, Gas, Nuclear, Hydro, Solar, Wind, Other)&lt;br/&gt;Period: January 2019 – present  |  Endpoint: electricity/rto/fuel-type-data&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Source 2 — ORNL Power Telemetry:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Per-node PSU input power (actual watts drawn from grid) and GPU power (job detection)&lt;br/&gt;Captured at 1-minute intervals from 4,626 computing nodes via BMC + NVIDIA DCGM"
      style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingRight=12;spacingTop=8;fontSize=12;verticalAlign=top;"
